de: SH/6/6 "Development of Sustainable Tourism Based on Provincial Values", Art. 3.8 and 9.3 - 13-12-2017 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Ungarn betreffend ein Projekt zur Förderung des nachhaltigen Tourismus aufgrund der natürlichen Werte und Potenziale der Region von Tisza
en: SH/6/6 "Development of Sustainable Tourism Based on Provincial Values", Art. 3.8 and 9.3 - 13-12-2017 - Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Hungary represented by the National Development Agency as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project "Development of sustainable tourism based on provincial values"
